{
  "stem": "747.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was indoors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If we would go, then I would never make it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just remember there was a staircase going down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's why I have this aversion of the stairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I-- whenever I see a staircase going down, with a-- with a railing in the side, I just can't-- I can't step on it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it brings back memories.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the rest, we didn't see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just we saw their bodies-- their naked bodies the following few hours later, or the following day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Matter of fact, one man-- his name was Press, Efraim Press.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went to school with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't talk to him, but I knew he was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was another man, his was Leo Horowitz, and he was newly married.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were sleeping in the same room in the ghetto, and we got on the same train, and we arrived the same time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His wife, her name was Ellie, Elli Spindler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was working with us on our old building crew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I was taken to clean the watchtowers, one day, I noticed, I-- I noticed-- the husband, Leo, working in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we started to talk-- you know, between the Nazis disappear, hear a snatch of conversation and there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, surely, he was working there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I ask him, tell me, is it true what they say that's happening in those?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, unfortunately, it is true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if I think about my parents-- had this horrible fate, I can't accept it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, unfortunately, people are killed here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he used to send messages with us to his wife and little packages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was the watchtower was so close-- like the window from here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was just-- just we-- from the watchtower, we talked.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
